name: PS-07-Voronoi-Flow_Radials
description: v4W.ENko - "PS-07-Voronoi-Flow_Radials". This Black&White  illustration is dedicated to the "Voronoi" flow of standards in patterns realized in 2d. The "Voronoi" diagram is used to generate the layer of white cells according to the re-parametrization of the "Substrate" pattern as well. "Voronoi" cells are transformed in real-time. The "radius" parameter of the "voronoi diagram" is used to generate the number of  offsets to concentrate the radials with the number of 14 using the "Gaussian" function this time. The whole visualizations is forming abstract motion image. 9 cells / random seed 3453.  Packed as GIF. 1024*1024px / 180 frames.
